Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking everywhere for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da. Now show me the other half \Nthat you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That map...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen now, Dororo. Remember this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your papa's lifelong ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry it on with you. And protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have that, Itachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you have something like this \Non your back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.57,0:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna see my back? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,See? No map anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not on his back, it's in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our only clue. We're taking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't stand a chance against my bro, \Nyou jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Still a chatty little brat, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:01:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:03:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,#16 The story of Shiranui
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to sleep. \NI got a job for you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to fill in \Nthe other half of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The place you're headed for, is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the place old man Hibukuro \Nhid the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an idea of what was going on \Neven when I was under him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The goods we stole from the samurai  \N went missing now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All good stuff worth money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be the thief was actually Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept my eye on him,  \N waiting for him to slip up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you gotta hand it to him.  \N That man never slips up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I was being paranoid  \N and stopped thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I became desperate for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I remembered it. \NI decided to just give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But Boss was long dead by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You two were the only ones who'd know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was heading for that temple  \N where we last met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I dug her grave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I turned her over \Nand saw this on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You dirty bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The dead can't use it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings won't get you any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,See that cape, Dororo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Hakkotsu Cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where your papa hid the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for you to do your part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a cut if you help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You could eat all you want then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your belly sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't me, that was the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, how do we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get there by land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need a boat to cross over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Must've been raided by brigands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The boats...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all been wrecked. Darn ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some boats?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some. Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. But it's gonna cost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you? \NWhere are the rest of the villagers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All dead. The brigands got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's not right about him. \NWe better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There ain't no other boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If he tries anything funny, \NI'll just kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the oarsmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said we needed any oars?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharks! They're pulling the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru and Saburomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You named them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharks are your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. See how powerful they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious about my arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I fed it to Jiromaru and Saburomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor things were so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He fed them his own arm? \NHe really is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,These two mean the world to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But now they've got a taste \Nfor human flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't eat anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I fed them dead bodies at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to give them something fresh, \Nso I snatched and fed them women and kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They grew bigger the more they ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They can devour a whole village now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole village? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there were no brigands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I fed them all to my babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the boat around, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru, Saburomaru. You two hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no normal sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat them all at once now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the rest for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburomaru, keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat the rest after sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't letting us get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess this is finally the end \Nfor the great Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I got away from the samurai, \Nonly to get eaten by sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai... Hey, Itachi. \NI thought you had it good with your lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I went off to war under his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked my ass off \Ntrying to win some ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, when are reinforcements coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are reinforcements coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They ain't. They ain't ever coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They all went to attack headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just a lure. \NWe were sent here to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To them, we aren't even human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No good comes from messing with samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I left them and \Nwent back to being a brigand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:14:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He went through all this trouble \Nto hide it. It's gotta be a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I could do anything I want to \Nwith that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But what a fleeting dream that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I never dug up your mama's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, ouch. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, right? \NThat means you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't act like you're already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived all on my own, \Neven without Papa and Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been through lots of tough days. \NAlmost died a few times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never gave up, \Nnever even complained.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I shrugged it all off and pushed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look down. Keep your head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a brigand, act like one \Nand hang on to life till your last breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of words for a little runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound just like your papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you heard the little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a man, \Nstand up and fight for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody still crying like a baby, \Nno sharks are gonna get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz I'll kill you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But Boss, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Dororo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm diving in to lure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull this rope up when I signal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The shark will jump up trying to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When it does, you all stab him at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll get it for sure. \NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo! That reckless kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it dead...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We... we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta reach the cape \Nbefore the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tear off the seats and use them as oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddle for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The idiot shark boy really came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You had the upper hand in the water. \NBut not up here on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've done enough. \NYou're going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost half of my men because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I could kill him a thousand times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Toss him somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, time for you to spill your guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb. \NTell us where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said I'd given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a whole fortune \Njust waiting for us to grab it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have on your back  \N can move people and change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a source of great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just force you to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let this be the end of me. \NI need one more shot at life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing on my back. You saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew. \NI wonder why Boss raised you as a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo, your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm her back by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how you hid it, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Papa's precious money...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How it must've hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How it must've pained you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru, eat them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love  \N this accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world  \N on our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be difficult for you \Nto travel without a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know of a man who goes around \Ngiving limbs to those who've lost theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think his name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Jiromaru"
